OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FVariable
OL,6,Fcloud and some clear spells. Mostly
OL,7,Fdry, although a few showers reaching
OL,8,Fthe far north towards dawn. Turning
OL,9,Fchilly in some rural spots, with winds
OL,10,Fremaining light.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FTurning cloudier for a time
OL,13,Fas scattered showers move south, with
OL,14,Fa cooler northerly breeze developing.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FBright
OL,17,For sunny spells and a chance of
OL,18,Fshowers each day, these more likely on
OL,19,FFriday. Cooler into midweek, with
OL,20,Fpatchy overnight rural frost possible,
OL,21,Fmilder later. Winds generally light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
